{"word":"H3510 - כָּאַב - kâʼab - kaw-ab' - Grieving","slug":"H3510","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּאַב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kâʼab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-ab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Grieving"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05D0;&#x05D1; - ka&#x0302;'ab</b> - <i>kaw-ab'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to feel <i>pain</i>; by implication to <i>grieve</i>; figuratively to <i>spoil: - </i>grieving, mar, have pain, make sad (sore), (be) sorrowful."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3511\">H3511</a>, <a href=\"#/H4341\">H4341</a>"}]}